OL,3,CEmergency mobile test next month will
OL,4,Cbe 'one of biggest drills in UK
OL,5,Chistory'
OL,7,FAn emergency alert drill in a month's
OL,8,Ftime "will be one of the biggest
OL,9,Fpublic safety exercises" in UK
OL,10,Fhistory, a Cabinet minister has said.
OL,12,FPat McFadden said mobile phone alerts
OL,13,Fcould save lives during raging storms
OL,14,For when wildfires break out.
OL,16,FOn Sunday September 7 at around 3pm,
OL,17,Fmobile phones connected to 4G and 5G
OL,18,Fnetworks will vibrate and emit a siren
OL,19,Fsound for up to 10 seconds.
