OL,7,FThe Government has previously used the
OL,8,Fsystem for real, including in January
OL,9,Fduring Storm Eowyn to warn people in
OL,10,FScotland and Northern Ireland about
OL,11,Fsevere weather.
OL,13,FApproximately 3.5 million people
OL,14,Facross Wales and south-west England
OL,15,Freceived an alert during Storm Darragh
OL,16,Flast December and a 500kg unexploded
OL,17,FSecond World War bomb found in a
OL,18,FPlymouth back garden triggered a
OL,19,Fwarning in February last year.
