OL,3,CEmergency mobile test next month will
OL,4,Cbe 'one of biggest drills in UK
OL,5,Chistory'
OL,7,F"From major storms to wildfires, this
OL,8,Fsystem could save your life in an
OL,9,Femergency," Mr McFadden said.
OL,11,F"Just like the fire alarm in your
OL,12,Fhouse, it's important we test the
OL,13,Fsystem so that we know it will work if
OL,14,Fwe need it.
OL,16,F"This test will be one of the biggest
OL,17,Fpublic safety exercises in our
OL,18,Fnation's history.
