OL,4,Cbe 'one of biggest drills in UK
OL,5,Chistory'
OL,7,FIt will read: "This is a test of
OL,8,FEmergency Alerts, a UK Government
OL,9,Fservice that will warn you if there's
OL,10,Fa life-threatening emergency nearby.
OL,12,F"You do not need to take any action.
OL,13,FIn a real emergency, follow the
OL,14,Finstructions in the alert to keep
OL,15,Fyourself and others safe.
OL,17,F"Find simple and effective advice on
OL,18,Fhow to prepare for emergencies at
OL,19,Fgov.uk/prepare.
